text: Dorjsembeegiin Erdenchimeg (born 14 January 1959) is a Mongolian archer. Erdenchimeg competed at the 1988 Summer Olympics.Dorjsembeegiin Erdenchimeg == References == Category:1959 births Category:Living people Category:Mongolian archers Category:Olympians for Mongolia
title: Dorjsembeegiin Erdenchimeg
